There is a lot going on in this accounts tab that could be better handled. One page (profile) with these other links found there! There is 
no benifit fo having them all here this way, it confuses the way you can use the menu, it would be faster and more orginised to have these
links all on one main profile page.

Also update/refraze some user preset messages, Ph7 has done an incredable job but english not being his mother tounge there are
always going to be grammer mistakes in these responses, they are small things like "Never send anybody the money". No "the" needed 
Only problemis the size of the file they are in is 15,159 lines long!!! This is a long job and requires lots of concentration. Its 
given me a headache more than once and you feel like you are not making any progress!

******************************************************
Add Uk phone number support (11 digits start with 0) -> changing following bellow in _protected/app/configs/config.ini (after install)
for preinstall the devloper Ph7 would need to add this to his install script (I will request at some point)

[validate]
phone.pattern = "^[0][1-9]\d{1}$|^[0]\d{10}$"

